flowchart LR
    A[Decision and credible alternatives] --> B[Define counterfactual, horizon, and population]
    B --> C[Estimate incremental costs and benefits]
    C --> D[Model bottlenecks, risk, adoption, and realization]
    D --> E[Scenario, sensitivity, break-even, and uncertainty analysis]
    E --> F{Approve?}
    F -->|No| G[Reject, defer, or redesign]
    G --> A
    F -->|Yes| H[Implement with value-realization plan]
    H --> I[Measure adoption, cost, outcomes, and released capacity]
    I --> J[Realization ledger and post-implementation review]
    J --> K{Continue?}
    K -->|Expand| H
    K -->|Modify or renegotiate| A
    K -->|Retire or replace| L[Decommission and preserve evidence]

    Q[Evidence strength, provenance, metric versions, and decision record] -. applies throughout .-> B
    Q -. applies throughout .-> E
    Q -. applies throughout .-> I
    Q -. applies throughout .-> L
